“I don’t know what he is talking about. I am just hearing it for the first time. I am not a thug and I don’t know thugs. You should ask Imuse to prove his case beyond doubt. People should not just make political statements and go into their house and sleep. I don’t know what he is talking about and in fact, it does not make any sense. Maybe he has just taken a bottle of ogogoro  and he doesn’t know what he is talking about. Is him you should interrogate more”, he said.‎
